{"tid":520529,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中二生厚德商場玩扶手梯 吊上1/F失手墮樓重傷","createTime":"2018-01-05T13:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T14:30:10.000Z","uid":150881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a797de44e3d8ec9919935b99fb2628936a4c0421","tid":520529,"uid":150881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T13:43:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180105&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57671228\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180105%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57671228&d=3G27iXfkleI%2BSqobtAB8jpzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=2d0da9f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180105%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57671228&h=4a22a4a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180105&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57671228</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳厚德商場發生中學生從扶手電梯墮下重傷意外！<br />\n<br />\n據現場消息稱，一名中學生今午約4時，在商場地下扶手<br />\n<br />\n電梯旁玩耍，其間嘗試用雙手掹著一邊扶手梯吊上1樓，<br />\n<br />\n可惜疑失手從高位墮下受傷，一度躺在地上毫無反應。<br />\n<br />\n事發救護員接報到場，用擔架床將男生抬走送院。事後<br />\n<br />\n在場的同學亦協助警員調查。<br />\n<br />\n據目擊者Tony表示，當時與朋友在商場一樓快餐店吃<br />\n<br />\n包，聽到外面有人大叫，於是走出餐廳查，則發現有一<br />\n<br />\n名穿校服的男生躺在樓下地面，相信他由扶手梯跌下，<br />\n<br />\n當時男生受傷不能動彈，其兩名女同學在旁不斷安慰。<br />\n<br />\n事後受傷男生的同學向《蘋果》提供一段事發時的片<br />\n<br />\n段，從片中可見，涉事男生當時雙手攀爬一邊扶手梯，<br />\n<br />\n儼如玩單杆姿勢，並隨扶手梯往上層一樓，當扶手梯差<br />\n<br />\n不多到達上層時，男童疑似「唔夠力」，一度起腳力<br />\n<br />\n撐，並欲伸手找住圍欄，可惜失手抓不到欄杆，整個人<br />\n<br />\n跌下。據受傷男生的同學表示，他在區內一間國際學校<br />\n<br />\n就讀中二，事發時與多名同學一齊。"},{"pid":"2b52598bcab37eb0ee2fd8ce9cf42e3c04dbd850","tid":520529,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T13:44:52.000Z","msg":"中二病"},{"pid":"3c6387dbe84e62a8d2cba1adea891941fbe66a71","tid":520529,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T14:27:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"229079f590e0a7c52a01e43098265cb0f824727d","tid":520529,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T14:29:52.000Z","msg":"國際學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蝻定死鬼仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aed43cda7d19d9f6ae1cc7f8fa704583ac76556","tid":520529,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T14:30:10.000Z","msg":"事後受傷男生的同學向《蘋果》提供一段事發時的片段<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}